      "name": "Construct stiffness QoI comparison — FEA vs. experiment",
      "description": "FEA-predicted construct stiffness compared to N=11 experimental measurements. Mean error 4.2%; E/uval = 0.87 (< 1.96 acceptance threshold). UQ campaign (Latin Hypercube, 500 samples) confirmed stiffness sensitivity dominated by cortical bone modulus; all sensitivity indices reported in the accompanying technical report TR-2024-CB-001."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/validation/vr-yield-force-comparison",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Yield force QoI comparison — FEA vs. experiment",
      "description": "FEA-predicted yield force compared to N=11 experimental measurements. Mean error 6.8%; E/uval = 1.41 (< 1.96 acceptance threshold). Sensitivity analysis embedded in UQ campaign identified screw-rod interface friction coefficient as the dominant parameter; parametric sweep results tabulated in TR-2024-CB-001 Section 4."
    },
    {
